# Keep GitHub's language statistics focused on the actual source code,
# so the repo is correctly identified as a Python project rather than being
# dominated by the bundled public-domain novels and generated reports.
# These attributes affect GitHub's display only — they change no file contents.

data/**        linguist-vendored
datasets/**    linguist-generated
results/**     linguist-documentation
docs/**        linguist-documentation
*.md           linguist-documentation
